2. Prydo ID (Soulbound NFT)

Create a page where users can mint their Prydo ID.

Rules:
Only one Prydo ID per wallet.
This NFT is Soulbound (non-transferable).

Mint Phases:

Phase 1 (Genesis)
Supply: 100 NFTs
Price: Free

Phase 2 (Early Users)
Supply: 900 NFTs
70% free mint
30% minimal price

Phase 3 (Growth)
Supply: 10,000 NFTs
50% free mint

Phase 4 (Public)
Unlimited supply
20% free mint

Display mint progress and supply counters on the website.

