3. Identity Creation Page

After minting Prydo ID, users can create identity NFTs.

Two identity types:

Option A: Face NFT
Users upload a face photo.
AI converts it into a stylized NFT avatar.

Option B: Avatar NFT
Users generate avatars using traits.

Traits System:

Background
Skin
Hair
Eyes
Mouth
Outfit
Accessories
Aura

Example traits:

Background: Neon City, Galaxy, Matrix, Cyber Grid
Hair: Short Hair, Neon Hair, Cyber Spikes
Eyes: Normal Eyes, Laser Eyes, Robot Eyes
Outfit: Hoodie, Hacker Jacket, Armor
Accessories: Glasses, VR Headset, Crown
Aura: Fire Aura, Lightning Aura, Cosmic Aura

NFTs should be auto-generated from layered traits with rarity probabilities.

